---
---
<html lang="ja">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>阪急梅田本店 | Hankyu Umeda Main Store</title>
		<style>
			:root {
				--primary: #e60012; /* 阪急レッドを意識した鮮やかな赤 */
				--accent: #f8b500;
				--bg: #111111;
				--text: #ffffff;
			}
			body {
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				background-color: var(--bg);
				color: var(--text);
				font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN', 'Hiragino Sans', Meiryo, sans-serif;
				-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
			}
			header {
				padding: 1rem 5%;
				border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary);
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				align-items: center;
				background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
				position: sticky;
				top: 0;
				z-index: 100;
			}
			.logo {
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				font-weight: 900;
				letter-spacing: -1px;
			}
			.logo span {
				color: var(--primary);
			}
			nav a {
				color: white;
				text-decoration: none;
				margin-left: 20px;
				font-weight: 700;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
			}
			.hero {
				height: 80vh;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				justify-content: center;
				align-items: flex-start;
				padding: 0 10%;
				background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.8), transparent), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519125323398-675f0ddb6308?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80'); /* 仮画像 */
				background-size: cover;
				background-position: center;
			}
			.hero h1 {
				font-size: 5rem;
				line-height: 1;
				margin: 0;
				font-weight: 900;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: -2px;
				transform: skewX(-5deg);
			}
			.hero h1 span {
				display: block;
				color: var(--primary);
			}
			.hero .sub {
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				margin-top: 20px;
				border-left: 10px solid var(--primary);
				padding-left: 20px;
			}
			.section-title {
				padding: 4rem 10% 2rem;
				font-size: 3rem;
				font-weight: 900;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
			}
			.section-title::after {
				content: '';
				flex: 1;
				height: 2px;
				background: var(--primary);
				margin-left: 20px;
			}
			.grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
				gap: 20px;
				padding: 0 10% 4rem;
			}
			.card {
				background: #222;
				border: 1px solid #333;
				transition: transform 0.3s;
				position: relative;
				overflow: hidden;
			}
			.card:hover {
				transform: translateY(-10px);
				border-color: var(--primary);
			}
			.card img {
				width: 100%;
				height: 200px;
				object-fit: cover;
				filter: grayscale(100%);
				transition: 0.3s;
			}
			.card:hover img {
				filter: grayscale(0%);
			}
			.card-content {
				padding: 20px;
			}
			.card-tag {
				background: var(--primary);
				color: white;
				padding: 2px 10px;
				font-size: 0.7rem;
				font-weight: 900;
				display: inline-block;
				margin-bottom: 10px;
			}
			.card h3 {
				margin: 0;
				font-size: 1.2rem;
				font-weight: 900;
			}
			footer {
				background: #000;
				padding: 4rem 10%;
				text-align: center;
				border-top: 1px solid #333;
				font-size: 0.8rem;
				color: #666;
			}
			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				.hero h1 { font-size: 3rem; }
				.section-title { font-size: 2rem; }
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<header>
			<div class="logo">HANKYU<span>UMEDA</span></div>
			<nav>
				<a href="#">Shop</a>
				<a href="#">Event</a>
				<a href="#">Access</a>
			</nav>
		</header>

		<main>
			<section class="hero">
				<h1>WELCOME TO<span>THE NEXT STAGE</span></h1>
				<p class="sub">阪急梅田本店 | 常識を、超えてゆけ。</p>
			</section>

			<h2 class="section-title">Latest News</h2>
			<div class="grid">
				<div class="card">
					<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1441986300917-64674bd600d8?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="News 1" />
					<div class="card-content">
						<span class="card-tag">NEW ARRIVAL</span>
						<h3>2026 Spring Collection 公開</h3>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555529669-e69e7aa0ba9a?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="News 2" />
					<div class="card-content">
						<span class="card-tag">EVENT</span>
						<h3>9階 祝祭広場：ワールドフェア開催</h3>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1567401893414-76b7b1e5a7a5?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="News 3" />
					<div class="card-content">
						<span class="card-tag">FOOD</span>
						<h3>地下1階：限定スイーツセレクション</h3>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<h2 class="section-title">Events</h2>
			<div class="grid">
				<div class="card">
					<div class="card-content">
						<span class="card-tag">UPCOMING</span>
						<h3>梅田ファッションウィーク 2026</h3>
						<p style="color:#aaa; font-size:0.9rem; margin-top:10px;">開催期間：2026.05.01 - 05.10</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>

		<footer>
			&copy; 2026 HANKYU UMEDA MAIN STORE. ALL RIGHTS RESERVED.
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>
